data.name: textBox1.Text
data.value:
1. Connect the Power supply interface cable to OUTPUT1 +VE & -VE Ports of Power supply
2. Connect USB cable of lattice programmer to the online programmin jig.
3. Place the board in to the jig and lock testing jig
4. As per SIC configure the " DIAMOND PROGRAMMER " application and check the programming PASS or FAIL criteria.
